iv><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></li>
<li>
<p><strong>优点</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>灵活性</strong>：支持多种语法，包括模板字符串、CSS-in-JS 对象等。</li>
<li><strong>性能优化</strong>：提供了缓存机制，减少样式重新计算的次数。</li>
<li><strong>与 React 集成良好</strong>：支持 React 的所有功能，包括 Server-Side Rendering (SSR)。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>缺点</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>学习曲线</strong>：对于初学者来说，学习曲线可能较陡峭。</li>
<li><strong>调试难度</strong>：类似于 styled-components，调试生成的样式可能更困难。</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="_2-css-modules的使用" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-css-modules的使用"><span>2. CSS Modules的使用</span></a></h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>CSS Modules的定义</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>CSS Modules 是一种 CSS 文件的编写方式，通过将 CSS 类名局部化，避免了全局样式冲突。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>基本用法</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>创建 CSS Module 文件</strong>：</p>
<div class="language-css line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="css" data-title="css"><pre v-pre class="language-css"><code><span class="line"><span class="token comment">/* MyComponent.module.css */</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token selector">.button</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token property">background-color</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> blue<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token property">color</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> white<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token property">padding</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> 10px 20px<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token property">border</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> none<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token property">cursor</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> pointer<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token punctuation">}</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"> </span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token selector">.secondaryButton</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token property">background-color</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> white<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token property">color</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> black<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token property">padding</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> 10px 20px<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
