<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>配置 Babel Loader</strong>：</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="line"><span class="token comment">// webpack.common.js</span></span>
