<h3 id="_4-部署和维护" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-部署和维护"><span>4. 部署和维护</span></a></h3>
<p><strong>前端部署</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>构建生产环境代码</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>使用 npm run build 命令生成生产环境的构建文件。</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="line">npm run build</span>
<span class="line"><span class="token constant">AI</span>写代码javascript</span>
<span class="line">运行</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></li>
<li>
<p><strong>部署到静态网站托管服务</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Netlify</strong>：
<ol>
<li>注册 Netlify 账号。</li>
<li>连接 GitHub 仓库。</li>
<li>配置构建命令（如 npm run build）和发布目录（如 dist）。</li>
<li>选择域名并发布。</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li><strong>Vercel</strong>：
<ol>
<li>注册 Vercel 账号。</li>
<li>连接 GitHub 仓库。</li>
<li>配置构建命令（如 npm run build）和发布目录（如 dist）。</li>
<li>选择域名并发布。</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>部署到自己的服务器</strong>：</p>
<ol>
<li>将构建生成的 dist 目录上传到服务器的静态文件目录。</li>
<li>配置 Nginx 以提供静态文件服务。</li>
</ol>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="line">server <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  listen <span class="token number">80</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  server_name example<span class="token punctuation">.</span>com<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"> </span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  location <span class="token operator">/</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">    root <span class="token operator">/</span>path<span class="token operator">/</span>to<span class="token operator">/</span>dist<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">    try_files $uri $uri<span class="token operator">/</span> <span class="token operator">/</span>index<span class="token punctuation">.</span>html<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token punctuation">}</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token punctuation">}</span></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token constant">AI</span>写代码javascript</span>
<span class="line">运行</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>后端部署</strong></p>
<p><strong>使用 Docker</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>创建 Dockerfile</strong>：</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="line"><span class="token constant">FROM</span> <span class="token literal-property property">openjdk</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token number">11</span><span class="token operator">-</span>jre<span class="token operator">-</span>slim</span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token constant">COPY</span> target<span class="token operator">/</span>search<span class="token operator">-</span>app<span class="token punctuation">.</span>jar <span class="token operator">/</span>app<span class="token punctuation">.</span>jar</span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token constant">EXPOSE</span> <span class="token number">8080</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token constant">ENTRYPOINT</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token string">"java"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"-jar"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"/app.jar"</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token constant">AI</span>写代码javascript</span>
<span class="line">运行</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul>
<li><strong>构建 Docker 镜像</strong>：</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh" data-title="sh"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="line">mvn package </span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token function">docker</span> build <span class="token parameter variable">-t</span> search-app <span class="token builtin class-name">.</span></span>
<span class="line">AI写代码bash</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul>
<li><strong>运行 Docker 容器</strong>：</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh" data-title="sh"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="line"><span class="token function">docker</span> run <span class="token parameter variable">-p</span> <span class="token number">8080</span>:8080 search-app</span>
<span class="line">AI写代码bash</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>使用 Kubernetes</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>创建 Deployment 和 Service</strong>：</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="line"># deployment<span class="token punctuation">.</span>yaml</span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"></span>
